<div id="pf148c" class="pf w29 h12d" data-page-no="148c"><div class="pc pc148c w29 h12d"><div class="t m7d3 x13 h2f y1f10 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SABBATH SCHOOL LESSON QUARTERLY </div><div class="t m5 xa7 h2f y1fbe ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t me8a xba h4 y1fbe ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">25 </div><div class="t m1c58 xf h2f y14f3 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The hire of the laborers . . . crieth.&quot; </div><div class="t ma67 x16 h4 y1458 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">denous ulcers in their flesh, till it should be eaten away from </div><div class="t m6ff x16 h4 y117f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their bones.&quot;— </div><div class="t m3b6 x19 h30 y12a5 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Clarke. </div><div class="t m2b6 x61 h4 y15d2 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m131 xc h4 y986 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;And he doth not resist.&quot; The poor have no one to </div><div class="t m87 x16 h4 y1440 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">plead their cause while they are groaning under the load of </div><div class="t m1b14 x71 h4 y13b2 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">injustice and oppression. But if they wait patiently, the </div><div class="t m21fa x71 h4 y1102 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">One into whose ears their cry has entered will give justice </div><div class="t m114d x71 h4 y1144 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and equity to all. </div><div class="t ma2 x61 h4 y1188 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m19fe xc5 h4 y1057 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The reference to the early and the latter rain has a </div><div class="t mff2 x71 h4 y1441 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">broader application. The early rain was the rain of the </div><div class="t m8 x71 h4 y1fd3 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">seedtime, the latter rain was the rain of ripening for the </div><div class="t m6f0 x71 h4 y1110 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">harvest. The first fell in Judea about November; the second, </div><div class="t m22ae x71 h4 y1149 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">toward the end of April, when the ears of grain were filling. </div><div class="t m1934 x71 h4 y1461 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Without these, the earth would have been unfruitful. In like </div><div class="t mbfa x71 h4 y2047 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">manner, the former rain of the Spirit fell at Pentecost to </div><div class="t m2765 x71 h4 y1239 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">water the seed. The latter rain is to fall to ripen the harvest </div><div class="t m1bf2 x71 h4 y1dc7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the earth. We are to be patient until then. </div><div class="t m1cd x64 h4 y152f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m1722 xc5 h4 y1fb5 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In the time of trial, we are not to grow impatient, and </div><div class="t m1379 x71 h4 yfd6 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">seek, as many do. to right wrongs by resorting to force and </div><div class="t m71c x71 h4 y1123 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">questionable methods; but we should look forward patiently </div><div class="t mb92 x71 h4 y1522 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to the time when Jesus will come and render a just reward </div><div class="t mb81 x71 h4 y140e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to every man. </div><div class="t m1d0 x64 h4 y11c8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m1906 xc5 h4 y11c9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Groan not; grumble not; do not murmur through im-</div><div class="t m1774 x71 h4 y1f81 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">patience; and let not any ill treatment which you receive </div><div class="t mb76 x71 h4 ye04 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">induce you to vent your feelings in imprecations against your </div><div class="t m1054 x71 h4 y2078 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">oppressors. Leave all this in the hands of the Lord.&quot;— </div><div class="t m118e x75 h30 y2078 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Clarke. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
